data.description: Wonderful 4 large bedrooms 3 full baths. True office, formal living and formal dining for all those family gatherings.  This home has been well cared for and you will know when you walk through the door.  Beautiful kitchen has tons of storage and granite counter tops with center island for prepping and cookbook storage. Kitchen appliances have been updated. All bedrooms are large with walk in closets. Office has beautiful wood built-in shelves. The Den has lots of windows with beautiful plantation blinds. There is a large storm shelter in back yard. Nice flower beds and yard has sprinkler system. Nice neighborhood pool and clubhouse. Mustang School District. Super clean home that is ready for your family!
